How do you include external front and apply them?
Google font is libary of font.
It open source fonts that you can used in your webpage according to requirements.
It was launched in 2010
It contain 800 fonts.
It is free
 It is used to customized the font.
 
 ADDING METHOD
 =============
Step 1: Serach Google Fonts library
Step 2: Select the fonts .
Step 3: Adding the fonts to your project.
Step 4: Use the fonts in your CSS.
